    {
      "content": "Looking at the visualization summary for the Result Dataset output of our <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Execute R Script<ept id=\"p1\">][execute-r-script]</ept> module, you will see the 'Month' column is 'Categorical' with 12 unique values, again, just as we wanted.",
