    {
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">##&lt;a id=\"appendixb\"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</ph>APPENDIX B: Further reading\n\nThis R programming tutorial covers the basics of what you need to use the R language with Azure Machine Learning Studio.",
      "pos": [
        63906,
